The command [atscc] is a wrapper of convenience around [atsopt].

$ATSOPT = "atsopt"
$ATSCCOMP = "gcc -std=c99 -D_XOPEN_SOURCE"

-vats  : the version of atsopt
-tcats : typechecking only
-ccats : compiling ATS to C only

-DATS  : definition for [atsopt]
-DDATS : definition for [atsopt] and [atsccomp]
-IATS  : include path for [atsopt]
-IIATS : include path for [atsopt] and [atsccomp]
